The Salt Ponds Coalition was kind enough to provide the data included in
"demo_ww_data.csv" and "demo_ww_sites.csv". This data can be used to preview
WQdashboard or practice installing data, but should not be reposted without
permission from the Salt Ponds Coalition. These data use the Watershed Watch
data format. (RI_WW)

Learn more about the Salt Ponds Coalition:
https://saltpondscoalition.org/

Learn more about Watershed Watch:
https://web.uri.edu/watershedwatch/
